== 展覽 ==
從2014年開始，在日本各地、台灣、上海陸續舉辦展覽。除了名偵探柯南展、柯南咖啡廳，還有柯南音樂會等活動。為了紀念作者出生於[[鳥取縣|鳥取縣]]，不但在當地的路上隨處可見柯南的蹤跡，在校園、車站、圖書館裡也設有相關的銅像、圖案、海報等<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.conan-town.jp/contents/sec2_6.htm|title=Gosho Aoyama's Profile|accessdate=2011-03-19|publisher=Conan-Town.jp|language=ja|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20161103082307/http://www.conan-town.jp/contents/sec2_6.htm|archivedate=2016-11-03}}</ref><ref name="Museum">{{cite web|url=http://www.conan-town.jp/contents/sec2_1_5.htm|title=Aoyama World|accessdate=2011-03-19|publisher=Conan-Town.jp|language=ja|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20161105012640/http://www.conan-town.jp/contents/sec2_1_5.htm|archivedate=2016-11-05}}</ref><ref name="Statues">{{cite web|url=http://www.conan-town.jp/contents/sec2_1_2.htm|accessdate=2010-01-28|publisher=Conan-Town.jp|language=ja|script-title=ja:工藤新一の像|trans_title=Shinichi Kudo Statue|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20161103200350/http://www.conan-town.jp/contents/sec2_1_2.htm|archivedate=2016-11-03}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.conan-town.jp/contents/sec2_1_1.htm|accessdate=2010-01-28|publisher=Conan-Town.jp|language=ja|script-title=ja:コナンの像|trans_title=Conan Statue|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20161103084043/http://www.conan-town.jp/contents/sec2_1_1.htm|archivedate=2016-11-03}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.conan-town.jp/contents/sec2_1_6.htm|accessdate=2010-01-28|publisher=Conan-Town.jp|language=ja|script-title=ja:大栄小学校|trans_title=Taiei Elementary|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20161103083516/http://www.conan-town.jp/contents/sec2_1_6.htm|archivedate=2016-11-03}}</ref>。

=== 鳥取縣 ===
* {{nihongo|'''[[鳥取砂丘柯南機場|鳥取砂丘柯南機場]]'''|鳥取砂丘コナン空港}}
