=== 銷售成績 ===
《名偵探柯南》原作漫畫與相關書籍的總發行量超過1億5000萬本，成為{{tsl|en|List of best-selling manga|日本第七暢銷的漫畫系列作品}}<ref>{{cite web|url=http://prtimes.jp/main/html/rd/p/000000074.000001117.html|accessdate=2015-11-20|date=2015-03-26|work=PR Times|language=ja|script-title=ja:名探偵コナン ： 謎の「黒ずくめ」に迫る新章開幕　豪華オールスターで|archive-date=2020-04-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200413082808/https://prtimes.jp/main/html/rd/p/000000074.000001117.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>，其各冊單行本也時常名列於各大銷售排行榜<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.animenewsnetwork.com/news/2008-12-19/2008-yearly-japanese-comic-ranking-no.1-25|title=2008's Top-Selling Manga in Japan, #1–25|accessdate=2010-10-18|date=2008-12-19|publisher=[[Anime_News_Network|Anime News Network]]|archive-date=2016-02-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160203154047/http://www.animenewsnetwork.com/news/2008-12-19/2008-yearly-japanese-comic-ranking-no.1-25|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.animenewsnetwork.com/news/2010-06-02/top-selling-manga-in-japan-by-volume/1st-half-of-2010|title=Top-Selling Manga in Japan by Volume: 1st Half of 2010|accessdate=2010-10-18|date=2010-06-02|publisher=[[Anime_News_Network|Anime News Network]]|archive-date=2012-06-29|archive-url=https://archive.today/20120629025620/http://www.animenewsnetwork.com/news/2010-06-02/top-selling-manga-in-japan-by-volume/1st-half-of-2010|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2004年，本作的第一冊單行本連續三度登上美國《{{tsl|en|In the Shadow of No Towers|消失於黑影中的塔}}》的銷售排行<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.icv2.com/articles/home/5795.html|title=Spiegelman's 'No Towers' Tops BookScan List|accessdate=2013-01-01|date=2004-10-04|publisher=ICv2|archive-date=2013-12-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131203042424/http://www.icv2.com/articles/home/5795.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>，不久後也名列於《{{tsl|en|Diamond Comic Distributors|鑽石漫畫排行榜}}》之中<ref>{{cite web|url=http://icv2.com/articles/comics/view/5714/top-100-graphic-novels-actual-august-2004|title=Top 100 Graphic Novels Actual--August 2004|accessdate=2013-01-01|date=2004-09-20|publisher=ICv2|archive-date=2021-01-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210126112407/https://icv2.com/articles/comics/view/5714/top-100-graphic-novels-actual-august-2004|dead-url=no}}</ref>，其他冊別的單行本亦曾多次出現在《[[紐約時報暢銷書榜|紐約時報暢銷書榜]]》<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.nytimes.com/best-sellers-books/2010-11-07/manga/list.html|title=Best Sellers Manga|accessdate=2010-12-27|date=2010-11-07|publisher=[[The_New_York_Times|The New York Times]]|archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/5vS3xHqpp?url=http://www.nytimes.com/best-sellers-books/2010-11-07/manga/list.html|archivedate=2011-01-03|deadurl=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.nytimes.com/best-sellers-books/2011-05-01/manga/list.html|title=Best Seller Manga|accessdate=2012-09-30|date=2011-05-01|publisher=[[The_New_York_Times|The New York Times]]|archive-date=2016-03-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160306124424/http://www.nytimes.com/best-sellers-books/2011-05-01/manga/list.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.nytimes.com/best-sellers-books/2012-01-29/manga/list.html|title=Best Seller Manga|accessdate=2012-09-30|date=2012-01-29|publisher=[[The_New_York_Times|The New York Times]]|deadurl=no|archive-date=2016-02-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160225151104/http://www.nytimes.com/best-sellers-books/2012-01-29/manga/list.html}}</ref>。2010年12月，本作於日本一項由20至29歲的民眾投票選出「最希望繼續連載的漫畫」中，分別在男性和女性的部分獲得第三名與第一名<ref>{{cite web|url=http://cobs.jp/enquete/realranking/2011/01/22_1.html|accessdate=2011-01-23|date=2011-01-22|publisher=COBS online|language=ja|archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/5vyCOrelH?url=http://cobs.jp/enquete/realranking/2011/01/22_1.html|archivedate=2011-01-24|script-title=ja:【男性編】最終回を迎えてほしくないマンガランキング|trans_title=(Men's Edition) Which do you not want to see end Manga Poll|deadurl=yes}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://cobs.jp/enquete/realranking/2011/01/22_2.html|accessdate=2011-01-23|date=2011-01-22|publisher=COBS online|language=ja|archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/5vyDqJi3h?url=http://cobs.jp/enquete/realranking/2011/01/22_2.html|archivedate=2011-01-24|script-title=ja:【女性編】最終回を迎えてほしくないマンガランキング|trans_title=(Women's Edition) Which do you not want to see end Manga Poll|deadurl=yes}}</ref>。《日本經濟雜誌》從2010年1月開始公布（日本）國內前50名漫畫家的各作品累積銷量，青山剛昌於2011年9月以332萬本的總銷售量獲得第16名<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.animenewsnetwork.com/news/2011-08-05/top-50-manga-creators-by-sales-since-2010|title=Top 50 Manga Creators by Sales Since 2010|accessdate=2013-11-18|date=2011-08-06|publisher=[[Anime_News_Network|Anime News Network]]|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20111011161426/http://www.animenewsnetwork.com/news/2011-08-05/top-50-manga-creators-by-sales-since-2010|archivedate=2011-10-11|deadurl=no}}</ref>，該年本作以212萬餘本的銷量獲得第19名<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.animenewsnetwork.com/news/2011-11-30/top-selling-manga-in-japan-by-series/2011|title=Top-Selling Manga in Japan by Series: 2011|accessdate=2013-11-18|date=2011-12-01|publisher=[[Anime_News_Network|Anime News Network]]|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131013123424/http://www.animenewsnetwork.com/news/2011-11-30/top-selling-manga-in-japan-by-series/2011|archivedate=2013-10-13|deadurl=no}}</ref>；2012年以243萬餘本的銷量獲得第17名<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.animenewsnetwork.com/news/2012-12-02/30-top-selling-manga-in-japan-by-series/2012|title=30 Top-Selling Manga in Japan by Series: 2012|accessdate=2013-11-18|date=2012-12-03|publisher=[[Anime_News_Network|Anime News Network]]|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130618151720/http://www.animenewsnetwork.com/news/2012-12-02/30-top-selling-manga-in-japan-by-series/2012|archivedate=2013-06-18|deadurl=no}}</ref>；2013年則是以196萬餘本的銷量獲得第24名<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.animenewsnetwork.com/news/2013-12-01/top-selling-manga-in-japan-by-series/2013|title=Top-Selling Manga in Japan by Series2013|accessdate=2014-01-01|date=2013-12-01|publisher=[[Anime_News_Network|Anime News Network]]|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131202043338/http://www.animenewsnetwork.com/n