/kitte_hagaki/stamp/tokusyu/2006/h180403_t.html|archivedate=2010-12-08|deadurl=yes}}</ref>。

=== 評價 ===
在美國地區，{{tsl|en|Mania.com|Mania.com}}的{{tsl|en|Eduardo M. Chavez|愛德華多·M·查維茲}}、{{tsl|en|Lori Lancaster|洛瑞·蘭卡斯特}}和[[IGN|IGN]]的{{tsl|en|A. E. Sparrow|A·E·史派羅}}都給予《名偵探柯南》的劇情高度評價。史派羅認為本作結合了《[[叔比狗|叔比狗]]》與《[[福爾摩斯探案|福爾摩斯探案]]》的風格<ref name="IGN review vol.21">{{cite web|url=http://uk.comics.ign.com/articles/839/839503p1.html|title=Case Closed: Volume 21 Review|accessdate=2009-12-29|author=A. E. Sparrow|date=2007-12-04|publisher=[[IGN|IGN]]|archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/5vS3xHqqV?url=http://uk.comics.ign.com/articles/839/839503p1.html|archivedate=2011-01-03|deadurl=yes}}</ref>；蘭卡斯特則描述《名偵探柯南》是一部處處充滿懸疑、令人驚艷的作品，並指出每個案件都讓人不可思議、覺得有趣<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.mania.com/case-closed-season-1-collection_article_80374.html|title=Case Closed Season 1 Collection|accessdate=2010-11-28|author=Lori Lancaster|date=2008-09-12|publisher=Mania.com|archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/5vS3xHqss?url=http://www.mania.com/case-closed-season-1-collection_article_80374.html|archivedate=2011-01-03|deadurl=yes}}</ref>；查維茲也認同原作漫畫對全年齡的讀者極具吸引力<ref name="Mania review vol.1">{{cite web|url=http://www.mania.com/case-closed-vol-01_article_81858.html|title=Case Closed Vol. #01 review|accessdate=2009-12-29|author=Eduardo M. Chavez|date=2004-10-20|publisher=Mania.com|archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/5vS3xHqqN?url=http://www.mania.com/case-closed-vol-01_article_81858.html|archivedate=2011-01-03|deadurl=yes}}</ref>。2010年，本作被[[About.com|About.com]]評選為「最佳連載漫畫系列作品」之一，並稱之「少年漫畫中被低估的至寶」<ref>{{cite web|url=http://manga.about.com/od/recommendedreading/tp/Best-Continuing-Manga-Of-2010.01.htm|title=Best Continuing Manga of 2010|accessdate=2012-09-29|publisher=[[About.com|About.com]]|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120610190551/http://manga.about.com/od/recommendedreading/tp/Best-Continuing-Manga-Of-2010.01.htm|archivedate=2012-06-10}}</ref>。來自{{tsl|en|THEM Anime Reviews|THEM影評網}}的{{tsl|en|Melissa Sternenberg|梅麗莎·斯特嫩伯格}}稱讚其驚悚的情節與動畫<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.themanime.org/viewreview.php?id=704|title=''Detective Conan'' Review|accessdate=2012-11-04|last=Sternenberg|first=Melissa|publisher=THEM Anime|archive-date=2020-11-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201112013331/http://www.themanime.org/viewreview.php?id=704|dead-url=no}}</ref>，{{tsl|en|ActiveAnime|ActiveAnime}}的評論家們認為其複雜的人物設計和作品特有的魅力使之深受懸疑推理迷的喜愛；本作也被評選適合較為成熟的讀者及觀眾收看<ref>{{cite web|url=http://activeanime.com/html/2007/06/13/case-closed-season-2-vol-2-death-wears-a-blindfold/|title=CASE CLOSED SEASON 2 – VOL. 2: DEATH WEARS A BLINDFOL (despite the title, the comment is valid for the entire series|accessdate=2013-06-21|last=Campbell|first=Scott|publisher=activeAnime|archive-date=2013-12-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131212093522/http://activeanime.com/html/2007/06/13/case-closed-season-2-vol-2-death-wears-a-blindfold/|dead-url=yes}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://activeanime.com/html/2007/01/29/case-closed-2-cracking-the-perfect-alibi-case-2-advance-review/|title=CASE CLOSED 2: CRACKING THE PERFECT ALIBI (CASE 2) [ADVANCE REVIEW] (despite the title, the comment is valid for the entire series|accessdate=2013-06-21|last=Ellingwood|first=Holly|publisher=activeAnime|archive-date=2013-10-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131030212024/http://activeanime.com/html/2007/01/29/case-closed-2-cracking-the-perfect-alibi-case-2-advance-review/|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。

然而，本作改編的美國版本將內容本土化的作法飽受當地觀眾的批評，[[動畫新聞網|動畫新聞網]]的{{tsl|en|Carl Kimlinger|卡爾·金林格}}指出其改變某些日本文化的意涵，導致觀眾對劇中的案件調查、暗號手法理解困難<ref name="IGN 3.2">{{cite web|url=http://uk.dvd.ign.com/articles/822/822435p1.html|title=Case Closed – 3.2: Death Wears a Blindfold DVD Review|accessdate=2010-12-03|author=Jeffrey Harris|date=2007-09-27|publisher=[[IGN|IGN]]|archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/5vS3xHqt6?url=http://uk.dvd.ign.com/articles/822/822435p1.html|archivedate=2011-01-03|deadurl=yes}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.animenewsnetwork.com/review/case-closed/dvd-2|title=DVD 2.1 review|accessdate=2010-11-28|author=Carl Kimlinger|date=2006-12-31|publisher=[[Anime_News_Network|Anime News Network]]|archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/5vS3xHqsl?url=http://www.animenewsnetwork.com/review/case-closed/dvd-2|archivedate=2011-01-03|deadurl=yes}}</ref>。{{tsl|en|Carlo Santos|卡洛·桑托斯}}認為角色的特質和配音員密不可分，在檢閱完[[動畫新聞網|動畫新聞網]]發行的首張DVD之後，他表示雖然主要人物表現得像真人，但次要人物顯得不夠真實<ref name="ANN DVD 1 review">{{cite web|url=http://www.animenewsnetwork.com/review/case-closed/dvd-1|title=DVD 1: Secret Life of Jimmy Kudo review|accessdate=2010-11-28|author=Carlo Santos|date=2004-11-03|publisher=[[Anime_News_Network|Anime News Network]]|archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/5vS3xHqse?url=http://www.animenewsnetwork.com/review/case-closed/dvd-1|archivedate=2011-01-03|deadurl=yes}}</ref>。IGN的{{tsl|en|Chris Wyatt|克里斯·懷亞特}}給予劇中的案件正面評價，認為其類型與[[阿嘉莎·克莉絲蒂|阿嘉莎·克莉絲蒂]]的密室設定相似，他形容《名偵探柯南》如同《[[神探加傑特|神探加傑特]]》與《[[法網遊龍|法網遊龍]]》以動漫的形式結合一體<ref>{{cite web|url=http://uk.dvd.ign.com/articles/788/788270p1.html|title=Case Closed: The Exploits of Genius DVD review|accessdate=2010-12-03|author=Chris Wyatt|date=2007-05-14|publisher=[[IGN|IGN]]|archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/5vS3xHqsz?url=http://uk.dvd.ign.com/articles/788/788270p1.html|archivedate=2011-01-03|deadurl=yes}}</ref>；但他的同事{{tsl|en|Jeffrey Harris|傑佛瑞·哈里斯}}表示對其老梗枯燥的戲碼以及美版將部分角色改名感到惱人<ref name="IGN 3.2" />。

